---

<Layout
  title="Our Program · Casa da Nova Vida"
  description="A personalized residential healing program for 3-5 guests at a time, uncovering root causes and building a foundation for lasting transformation."
>
  <!-- ===================== HERO (image + title only) ===================== -->
  <PageHero
    eyebrow="Our Program"
    title="What to Expect"
    image="/images/photos/cards/program-hero.jpg"
    imageAlt="A forest path lit by golden sunrise light"
  />

  <!-- ===================== LEAD + STATS ===================== -->
  <section class="px-6 py-16 lg:px-10 lg:py-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
      <p class="eyebrow">Room to breathe</p>
      <p class="mt-5 font-display text-2xl leading-[1.5] text-cocoa sm:text-3xl sm:leading-[1.45]">
        Healing requires a <span class="text-pine">conscious breath</span>. We
        give our guests time and space, outside the everyday, to reflect and
        integrate, through spiritual work, therapy, and community.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div
      class="mx-auto mt-14 grid max-w-4xl gap-8 border-t border-sand pt-12 text-center sm:grid-cols-3 sm:divide-x sm:divide-sand lg:mt-16 lg:pt-14"
    >
      <div>
        <p class="font-display text-4xl text-clay">3-5</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-stone">Guests at a time</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="font-display text-4xl text-clay">4-6</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-stone">Weeks, with room to extend</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="font-display text-4xl text-clay">1:1</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-stone">Integration coaching</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===================== CURRICULUM (roadmap) ===================== -->
  <section class="border-y border-sand bg-cream px-6 py-20 lg:px-10 lg:py-28">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
      <div class="text-center">
        <p class="eyebrow">Our Curriculum</p>
        <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl text-pine sm:text-4xl">A path to the root, step by step</h2>
        <p class="mx-auto mt-5 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed text-cocoa">
          Lasting healing begins by uncovering the root causes beneath the
          behavior. We walk each guest through this journey, at a pace that
          honors the work.
        </p>
      </div>

      <ol class="relative mx-auto mt-16 max-w-xl space-y-9 border-l-2 border-sand">
        {
          curriculum.map((c, i) => (
            <li class="relative pl-12">
              <span class="absolute left-0 top-0 flex h-10 w-10 -translate-x-1/2 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-pine font-display text-linen shadow-sm ring-4 ring-cream">
                {i + 1}
              </span>
              <h3 class="text-lg text-forest">{c.title}</h3>
              <p class="mt-1.5 text-sm leading-relaxed text-cocoa">{c.body}</p>
            </li>
          ))
        }
      </ol>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===================== PRACTICE PHOTO BAND ===================== -->
  <section class="px-6 lg:px-10">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl overflow-hidden rounded-[1.75rem] shadow-lg">
      <img
        src={withBase("/images/photos/life/practice-meditation.jpg")}
        alt="Guests and a coach meditating together on blankets beneath a Hill Country oak"
        class="h-64 w-full object-cover sm:h-80 lg:h-[26rem]"
        loading="lazy"
      />
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===================== TOOLS & PRACTICES (was Activities) ===================== -->
  <section class="px-6 py-20 lg:px-10 lg:py-28">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">
        <p class="eyebrow">Tools &amp; practices</p>
        <h2 class="mt-4 text-3xl text-pine sm:text-4xl">Ways we support your integration</h2>
        <p class="mt-5 leading-relaxed text-cocoa">
          A growing set of modalities we draw on to calm the nervous system and
          deepen recovery. We tailor them to each guest, and add more as we grow.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-14 grid gap-5 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
        {
          activities.map((a) => (
            <div class="group flex items-start gap-4 rounded-2xl border border-sand bg-linen p-6 transition-shadow duration-300 hover:shadow-[0_16px_40px_-24px_rgba(43,54,70,0.35)]">
              <div class="flex h-12 w-12 flex-none items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-cream to-sage/40 text-pine ring-1 ring-sand">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="h-6 w-6" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path d={a.icon} />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-base text-forest">{a.title}</h3>
                <p class="mt-1 text-sm leading-relaxed text-cocoa">{a.body}</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          ))
        }
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===================== NUTRITION ===================== -->
  <section class="bg-forest px-6 py-20 text-linen lg:px-10 lg:py-28">
    <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-6xl items-center gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-16">
      <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-[1.75rem] shadow-xl">
        <img
          src={withBase("/images/photos/cards/food.jpg")}
          alt="A spread of fresh, seasonal whole foods on a wooden table"
          class="h-72 w-full object-cover sm:h-96 lg:h-[30rem]"
          loading="lazy"
          width="1024"
          height="768"
        />
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow text-gold">Nutrition</p>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-sagelight">
          We serve healthy, organic, seasonal meals designed to stabilize and
          nourish body, mind, and emotions. And we teach the fundamentals of
          shopping, cooking, and intentional eating, so a healthy relationship
          with food continues long after you leave.
        </p>
        <blockquote class="mt-8 border-l-2 border-gold/60 pl-6 font-display text-2xl italic leading-relaxed text-gold sm:text-3xl">
          “Let food be thy medicine and medicine be thy food”
          <cite class="mt-3 block font-sans text-sm not-italic uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-sage">
            Hippocrates
          </cite>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===================== APPLY ===================== -->
  <section class="px-6 py-20 text-center lg:px-10 lg:py-28">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl">
      <h2 class="text-3xl text-pine sm:text-4xl">Interested in becoming a guest?</h2>
      <a
        href={withBase("/apply")}
        class="mt-9 inline-flex rounded-full bg-pine px-8 py-4 font-medium text-linen transition-colors hover:bg-forest"
      >
        Apply to become a guest
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="pb-20 lg:pb-28"><CTABand /></div>
</Layout>
